  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Hauliers and commercial drivers: you will need new documents to transport goods into the EU after Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">A summary of the driver, vehicle, cargo and customs documents required to transport goods into the EU after Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

