<div class="call-to-action">
<h2 id="stay-up-to-date">Stay up to date</h2>

<p>The <abbr title="United kingdom">UK</abbr> will leave the <abbr title="European Union">EU</abbr> on 31 October. This page tells you how to prepare for Brexit. It will be updated if anything changes, including if a deal is agreed.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/email/subscriptions/new?default_frequency=daily&topic_id=find-brexit-guidance-for-your-business-in-the-following-category-road-passengers-and-freight">Sign up for email alerts</a> to get the latest information.</p>
</div>

<h2 id="download-the-border-readiness-leaflet">Download the border readiness leaflet</h2>

<p>The information in the downloadable leaflet is the same as the information on this web page. Download the leaflet if you want to save or print a copy of the information.</p>

